{"article_id":"SdvjGjuTy9qEh4oF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton has been dogged for nearly a year by speculation","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"that she could be indicted by federal prosecutors for compromising classified information in her use of a private server","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"while she was secretary of State .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"FBI Director James Comey announced Tuesday","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"that he would not recommend charges in the case .","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Here ' s how it all started :","depth":2},{"id":6,"text":"March 2 , 2015 :","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The New York Times reports","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that Hillary Clinton used a private email server","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"while serving as secretary of State .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"March 10 , 2015 :","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Clinton defends her use of a private server ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"it was for \" convenience \"","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"so she could use one device for personal and business use .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" `` Looking back ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"it would have been better for me to use two separate phones and two separate e-mail accounts , ''","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` I thought","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"using one device would be simpler .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Obviously , it has n't worked out that way . ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"July 24 , 2015 :","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The inspectors general at the State Department and Director of National Intelligence ask the Justice Department to review","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"whether classified information was compromised in Clinton ' s use of private email .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"August 2015 :","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"A federal official confirms","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the FBI is investigating .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Aug. 11 , 2015 :","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Clinton ' s campaign says","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"she has directed","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that her server be turned over to the Justice Department .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Hillary Clinton to hand over email server to Justice Dept .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"May 25 , 2016 :","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"The inspector general at the State Department issues a report critical of Clinton ' s use of private email ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"department policies","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"dating to 2005","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"require","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that \" normal day-to-day operations \" be conducted on government computers .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"July 1 , 2016 :","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Attorney General Loretta Lynch says","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"she will accept recommendations from the FBI and career prosecutors in the email case in an attempt","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"to dispel criticism of her potential conflict of interest","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"after she met with former president Bill Clinton on a Phoenix tarmac .","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"AG Lynch will accept decision of FBI , prosecutors on Clinton email probe","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"July 2 , 2016 :","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Clinton is interviewed by the FBI for 3-1/2 hours in Washington , D.C .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"FBI , Clinton talk for 31⁄2 hours over emails","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"sent on private server","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"July 5 , 2016 :","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"FBI Director James Comey announces the recommendation","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"not to prosecute Clinton .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"FBI :","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Clinton faces no charges over e-mail ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"but acted 'carelessly '","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":109,"left":59,"right":108,"rela